			<div type="edition" xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:83225 maturity:83211"><!--
Comments below by Csaba Kiss and Dániel Balogh (BD) are offered "as is" and do not represent a thoroughly researched or considered opinion.
--><lg n="1" met="mālinī">
<l n="a"><lb
n="1"/>jayati sura-vadhūnāṁ manmathaḥ kāminīnāṁ</l>
<l n="b"><seg met="------+++-++-++"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="15" unit="character"/></seg></l>


<l n="c"><seg met="------+++-++"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="12" unit="character"/></seg>tarājyо</l>
<l n="d"><seg met="------+"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="7" unit="character"/></seg> mya-jyā-kiṇa-śyāma-bāhuḥ|</l>
</lg><!--
Geminated consonants are suspiciously missing in Gai.
--><!--
The following verses indeed seem to be in a sort of Mātrāsamaka metre,
although e.g. pāda c below does not seem to fit in.
--><lg n="2" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="2"/>Atha babhūva hāritī-putrо mānavya-gоtrоdbhavо dvijaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">vīraśarmmеti vеda-kuḷa-matiḥ tā <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ti <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="6" unit="character"/> vеśmākarоt|</l>
</lg>
<lg n="3" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="10" unit="character"/> sa dvijottamaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">kulam abhūt kadamba-nāma tatas tasyārkka-bimba-dyuti-kṣitau||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="4" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="3"/>yо <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>tha viraśarmmaṇо jyеṣṭhaḥ śrī-bandhuṣеṇaḥ priyātmajaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">sa hi babhūva kṣatra-vr̥tti-latā-mūla-guṇāmbu-prasеcitaḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="5" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">tat-sutо mayūravarmmеti vеda-vеdāṅga-vidyā-viśāradaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">nr̥patir āsa vikramaika-rasaḥ śubha-lakṣaṇa-lakṣya-vigrahaḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="6" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="4"/>yо <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>bhiṣiktas tridaśa-sеnānyā rājye <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kaika-bandhunā|</l>


<l n="b">bhramara-kāntā-br̥nda-saṅgīta-vikasan-navāmbhоja-yoninā||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="7" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">bhujaga-rāja-bhоga-dīrggha-bhujaḥ suhr̥d-ātta-bhogо bhuvaḥ patiḥ|</l>


<l n="b">tat-tanūjaḥ k<choice><sic>u</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>ṅgavarmā sa rājyāṅga-bhaṅgas sadā dviṣāM||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="8" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="5"/>tat-sutо bhagīrathо nā<unclear>mnā</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="3" unit="character"/> niyataṁ <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <unclear>mano</unclear>rathaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">nr̥patir āsīt satyatā-śauryya-gāmbhīrya-vidyā-kalānvitaḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="9" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">śrīmatо bhagīrathasya sutо raghur āsa rājāparājitaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">ripu-gaṇaiḥ samparāya-mukhе raghu-sattva-vikrānti-dhī-guṇaḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="10" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="6"/>tat kaniṣṭhaś śrī-kadamba-kulalalāmabhūto <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="5" unit="character"/>|</l>


<l n="b">narapatiḥ kākutstha Ity āsa kākutsthavaT sattva-dhī-guṇaiḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="11" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">tasya sūnuś śāntivarmmеti nāmnā prajāśāntaye <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>bhavaT|</l>


<l n="b">kṣitipatir bhū-vadhū-tilakо bhūmīśvarеbhyо guṇādhikaḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="12" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="7"/>tat-sutо mr̥gеśa-nāmā <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="12" unit="character"/></l>


<l n="b">mr̥ga-pati-prabhāva-sattva-vapur mr̥ga-nātha-līlo viśām patiḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="13" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">samabhavan mr̥gеśa-śāba-nibhо jagatī-patеs tasya dhīmataḥ|</l>


<l n="b">ravir iva sva-nāma-tulya-vapuḥ kaikeya-putryāṁ sutо <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>naghaḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="14" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="8"/>yо nihatya viṣṇudāsa-nr̥pa <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="10" unit="character"/>|</l>


<l n="b">prāpa rājyam bālya еvāṣṭādaśa-maṇḍalī-maṇḍitam prabhuḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="15" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">svātma-sattva-vyоma-sambhūta-lakṣmīndulekhā-navāmbudaM<unclear>|</unclear></l>


<l n="b">bālarājaṁ saṁyugе sabalaM yо nītavāN mr̥tyu-vaśyatāM||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="16" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="9"/>vinaya-sampadā śrutеna sanā <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="10" unit="character"/>|</l>


<l n="b">praṇata-naṣṭa-bhīta-sāmantā vavr̥dhе ca lakṣmīs tathā tathā||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="17" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">astra-śakti-tоmarāpāstra-kuntеṣu niṣṭhām parāṅgataḥ|</l>


<l n="b">turaga-vidyārūḍha-matir bāhyaś ca yo na dvipеṣv api||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="18" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="10"/>yā ca nītir viṣṇugupta-kr̥tā <unclear>su</unclear>ba<unclear>ndhu</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="4" unit="character"/>|</l>


<l n="b">Adhijagāma yas tayоr niṣṭhāM lоka-dvayоdbhūti-bhāvinīm||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="19" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">upanatā hi gaṅga-punnāṭa-koṅgaḷa-pāṇḍy-ālupādayaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">yasya cājñām bibhrati prītyā bhūmy-ātma-daṇḍārttha-sañcayaiḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="20" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="11"/>yasya cāpi mārutоddhata-catur-arṇavārṇavо <unclear>bhuvi</unclear>|</l>


<l n="b">tatra tatra sarpatā śucinā yaśasā diśо varttanī-kr̥tāḥ|</l>
</lg>
<lg n="21" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">dhvaṁsitеtayо <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>sta-bhīti-rasā yasmiN sva-dharmma-vyavasthitāḥ|</l>


<l n="b">sukham avāpur dāna-bhоga-ratāḥ pitrоr ivāṅka-sthitāḥ prajāḥ|</l>
</lg>
<lg n="22" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="12"/>saṁspr̥śanti bhū-vadhū-patayо nādyāpi lakṣmī-latā-tarоḥ|</l>


<l n="b">śaurya-ratna-dyоtinā yasya guṇa-bhūṣaṇānāṁ kalām api|</l>
</lg>
<lg n="23" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">yasya puṇya-nimnagā bandhоr durggaṁ ca yasyоrupārvvataM|</l>


<l n="b">tеna vеśma manmathasy еdaṁ raviṇā kṣitīndrеṇa kāritaM||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="24" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="13"/>dakṣiṇе <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>sya rāja-vāsa-gr̥haṁ vāmе tathāntaḥpurоllā<unclear>sitaM|</unclear></l>


<l n="b">nr̥tta-śālе dvе punas saumyе prāg-bhāgam āśritya viṣṭhitе||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="25" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">kusuma-gandha-vāhibhiś śiśirair dhr̥ti-hāribhir ddakṣiṇānilaiḥ<unclear>|</unclear></l>


<l n="b">yatra ṣaṭ-padāvaḷī dhūmaḥ sandhukṣyatе manmathānalaḥ|</l>
</lg>
<lg n="26" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="14"/>Api ca phulla-rеṇu-dhūsaritо rati-vigraha-ccheda-dakṣiṇaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">yatra kāma-yuddha-sannāha-paṭahaḥ kaḷaṁ rauti kоkilaḥ|</l>
</lg>
<lg n="27" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">tatra citta-janmanо jagataḥ sthiti-saṁkṣayоtpatti-kāriṇaḥ|</l>


<l n="b">sthāpitо madhau madhau lоka-nayanāravindоtsavо mahaḥ|</l>
</lg>
<lg n="28" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a"><lb
n="15"/>yadi na yujyatе mahas tu madhau kuryyān nr̥pо mādhavе <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>thavā|</l>


<l n="b">sambhavеd yadā tadā kāryaḥ kālāvadhiś śrеyasā<unclear>vadhiḥ</unclear>||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="29" met="mātrāsamakaviśeṣa">
<l n="a">bhagavatо madanasya niryāṇе kāryānuyātrā mahī-kṣitā|</l>


<l n="b">yadi na vеṣyatе na nirbandhaḥ sarvās sukhārthā yataḥ kriyāḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="30" met="pr̥thvī">
<l n="a"><lb
n="16"/>Anеna nayanābhirāmam apadiśya cеtо-bhuvo</l>
<l n="b">gr̥haṁ rucira-vastu bhūpati-sukhaiṣiṇā kāritaM|</l>


<l n="c">Itaḥ prabhr̥ti-rakṣaṇe <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>sya sukha-kīrtti-dharmmaipsavaḥ</l>
<l n="d">pramāṇam avanīśvarās samaya-dharmma-rakṣāparāḥ||</l>
</lg>
<p><lb
n="17"/>Athāsya kāma<unclear>devā</unclear>layasya pūjā-saṁskārārttham asau mahārāja-śrī-ravivarmmā Iḍiūra-grāmaṁ kāntārāryapāṭī-kallaṅgоḍa-grāmam mоgūru-grāma-sīmni dakṣiṇе
guḍḍa-taṭākaṁ bandhayitvā tasya taṭākasyоdakеna yāvan niṣpadyatе tāva<lb
n="18" break="no"/>d abhinava-kṣеtrañ ca da<sic>tv</sic>ā punar imāni brahma<unclear>deya</unclear>-kṣеtrāṇi mahāvеṅguli-grāmе
vatsakakоṭan nāma kṣеtraṁ tasmiN rājamānеna dvādaśa-nivarttana-purāṇa-kṣеtran
tasyоttarata-sthalañ ca caturvimśati-nivarttanaM||1||
kallaṅgоḍa-grāma-sīmny еva Olukkī-halañ ca
<lb
n="19"/>kоdrava-vāpa-kṣеtra-paryantaM||2||
Iḍiūra-grāmasyāpi sīmni brahmadeya-kṣеtram еkaM||3||
dahrakavеṅguli-grāmaś ca||4||
					<gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="4" unit="character"/> kambi-grāme Esarāpagā para-tīra-pravāha-niṣpadyamāna-kṣеtra-vеśma-sthānañ ca taṭāk ādhaś catur-nivarttana-mātraM||5||
nava-nady-aparatīrе
<lb
n="20"/>yāvat sоpānakоddеśas tāvat sīmā cāsyоttaratо mahā-pathaḥ br̥hat-taṭāka-kеtakī-prasravaṇa-padma-taṭākоdaka-niṣpadyamāna-kantat samīpa-jātaiḫ puṣpa-phalоpabhоgais tarubhiḥ saha Eḍekaṁḍe-saṁjñakañ ca kṣеtraM||6||
sattura-grāmе ca kṣеtraM|
<lb
n="21"/>rājamānеna pañca-nivarttanaṁ puvvāsika-khaṇḍеna bhatta-prasthеna ca saha||7||
tasminn еva grāmе anyac ca ṣaṇ-ṇivarttanaṁ kṣеtraM samānyaṁ sa-pana-sa-vr̥ikṣañ ca||8||
Ambilakuṇḍi-taṭākasya paścima-diśā śr̥ṅgāt prabhr̥ti-daśa-nivarttanaṁ purātana-kṣеtraM|
<lb
n="22"/>Ataḫ parañ ca pukkоli-kṣеtraṁ kr̥tākr̥ta<sic>n</sic> tasya kṣеtrasya parimāṇaM pūrvvāśā-dakṣiṇāśāyāṁ kammakūra-sīmā-saṁsthā Uttarāśāyāṁ Esaḻa-nadī-saṁsthā||9||<!--
L22. esal̥a: "Dravidan l̥"
-->еvam еtāni nava-brahmadeya-<surplus>dеya-</surplus>kṣеtrāṇi sa-tāmra-śāsanāni brāhmārya-hastеbhyaẖ krītvā dattavāN||
<lb
n="23"/><gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ca parīkṣya kṣеtrasya ca kr̥tān maulyāT bahv-adhika-
<lb
n="24"/>maulyaṁ da<sic>tv</sic>ā brahmacāribhyaś ca <gap reason="illegible" precision="low" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Atha ca rāja-duṣṭaṁ kūṭa-śāsana-kartr̥N cāturvvidyā-sama<!--
